WHEN there is replica of a component, whether API or cache or DB, we will use load balancer.

However API gateway is just to forward request to individual services, so that client does not have to know all IPs of services. This achieves abstraction.

Virtual Private Cloud will have Gateways and Services
Design patterns for Microservices
- SAGA (ex swiggy)
- Ochestrator
- choreographer

Observer design pattern for Kafka